reviewText: Very insightful delivery of the pertinent message on the life of Jonathan, which is usually lost when discussing David and Saul's relationship. Gave me a new desire to study the life of Jonathan and to try to avoid making the same mistakes he made. What an awesome message.

THIS SERIES IS VERY INFORMATIVE AND PRICELESS DVD 1 SAUL'S SUICIDE DVD 2 JONATHAN'S JUDGEMENT DVD 3 TALK ME THROUGH IT. IN SUMMATION IT TALK'S ABOUT HOW WE CAN LEARN FROM THE MISTAKES SAUL MADE INCLUDING HIS SUICIDE AND HOW WE SHOULD REPENT, HOW JONATHAN LISTENED TO HIS FLESH INSTEAD OF HIS SPIRIT WHICH WAS ULTIMATELY FATAL AND BUY THE DVD FOR THE REST YOU WILL NOT REGRET IT.
